### EC-OPS — Validation & Error Scenarios
### Every request below should return 4xx — confirms the API boundary holds
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8002


# ── 422 Input validation ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Empty customer_name → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "",
  "items": [{ "product_name": "Widget", "quantity": 1, "price": "9.99" }]
}

###

### Whitespace-only customer_name → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "   ",
  "items": [{ "product_name": "Widget", "quantity": 1, "price": "9.99" }]
}

###

### Empty items array → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Alice",
  "items": []
}

###

### Empty product_name → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Alice",
  "items": [{ "product_name": "", "quantity": 1, "price": "9.99" }]
}

###

### Zero quantity → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Alice",
  "items": [{ "product_name": "Widget", "quantity": 0, "price": "9.99" }]
}

###

### Negative quantity → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Alice",
  "items": [{ "product_name": "Widget", "quantity": -5, "price": "9.99" }]
}

###

### Negative price → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Alice",
  "items": [{ "product_name": "Widget", "quantity": 1, "price": "-1.00" }]
}

###

### Missing required field (no customer_name) → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [{ "product_name": "Widget", "quantity": 1, "price": "9.99" }]
}

###

### Missing required field (no items) → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Alice"
}

###

### Wrong type — quantity as string → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Alice",
  "items": [{ "product_name": "Widget", "quantity": "one", "price": "9.99" }]
}


# ── 404 Not found ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get non-existent order → 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###

### Delete non-existent order → 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###

### Invalid UUID format → 422
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/not-a-uuid


# ── 409 Conflict ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Cancel a non-PENDING order → 409
### First create an order and wait 5 min for scheduler to promote it to PROCESSING,
### then paste that order ID here.
@processingOrderId = REPLACE_WITH_PROCESSING_ORDER_ID

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{processingOrderId}}
